INSERT INTO blogPosts (title, slug, excerpt, content, category, tags, authorId, authorName, authorCredentials, readTime, viewCount, isPublished, publishedAt, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES ('Optimizing SBRT Treatment Planning for Lung Cancer: A Practical Guide', 'optimizing-sbrt-lung-cancer-treatment-planning', 'Comprehensive strategies for achieving optimal dose distribution and minimizing toxicity in stereotactic body radiation therapy for lung cancer patients.', '# Optimizing SBRT Treatment Planning for Lung Cancer

SBRT has revolutionized early-stage NSCLC treatment. This guide explores evidence-based strategies for optimizing treatment planning.

## Key Planning Objectives

- Tumor Coverage: 95-99% PTV coverage
- Dose Conformity: CI of 1.0-1.2
- Gradient Index: GI < 5.0
- OAR Sparing: Strict dose constraints

## Conclusion

Optimizing SBRT requires meticulous attention to target delineation, dose prescription, and quality assurance.', 'clinical-practice', 'SBRT, lung cancer, treatment planning', 1, 'Dr. Sarah Chen', 'MD, DABR', 8, 0, 1, '2025-01-15', NOW(), NOW())
